Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:25.23,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛が愛を「重過ぎる」って理解を拒み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:29.69,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}憎しみに　変わっていく前に…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}何もかもそうだろ?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:36.82,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}バツの悪い事情にはいつも蓋して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}食わせ物のリアル
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}歪んだジレンマ時代で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.91,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}約束したはずの二人さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.96,0:01:50.29,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}気付かず通り過ぎて行く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:57.72,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}壊しあって　解り合ってたことも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}置き去りにした
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:03.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}これが成れの果てなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:07.48,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}認めないで　立ち向かったときも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:13.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちて行く時のイメージから逃げ出せずに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:18.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Ah　何度でも探し出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:25.24,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君の目　その手の温もりを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:28.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}愛はいつも私を傷つけるだけ…って
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:32.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君はつぶやいて　信じる事が
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.42,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}怖くて泣いたんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.55,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}弱さを知って強くなれ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}恐れず信じることで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:46.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}本当の愛を知るのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.39,0:01:25.23,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}爱因爱而愈加沉重 却拒绝理解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:29.69,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在爱变为恨之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.69,0:01:31.77,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}所有一切皆是如此吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.77,0:01:36.82,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}窘迫的永远是这眼前的迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.86,0:01:39.66,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}仿佛被吞噬之物的写实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:41.95,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在这被扭曲的进退两难之时代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:45.91,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使海誓山盟的两人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:50.29,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也渐行着冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.96,0:01:57.72,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}毁灭与理解之物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.80,0:01:59.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}早已被遗弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:03.10,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}这难道是灭亡之尽头？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:07.48,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}否认这一切 挺身面对之时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:13.90,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即将殒落之时 都不会逃离眼前的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:18.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}啊，无论如何也要找寻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:25.24,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}你的双眸 双手的温存
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.37,0:02:28.75,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}说什么「爱总是只给我带来伤害」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.75,0:02:32.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}君之低声细语 深信之言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.42,0:02:35.42,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}是在恐惧中哭泣么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.55,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}认识着软弱 渴望着坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:41.39,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当不再恐惧而满怀信仰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.39,0:02:46.18,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}那将是真实的爱
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:56.86,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}純真さが シンプルな力に 変わる 世界に影をつくりだす
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:11.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ガラスケ一スに横たわる 光の存在に触れたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:18.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}振り上げた手 降ろせなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:27.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}落ちるようにしゃがみこんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:35.49,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 明日の理想だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:42.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}語り継ぐような 美談にもならないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:50.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}この体を失いそうな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:59.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}ギリギリの場所が 哀しいくらい似合ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.43,0:21:56.86,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}当纯真变为单纯的力量 世界由此诞生了影子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.53,0:22:11.42,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}穿透过玻璃橱 感触着这光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.50,0:22:18.51,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}举起的手无法放下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:27.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}却如同坠落般跌下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.31,0:22:35.49,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}Prototype boy 抛开明天的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:42.99,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即便无法成为传承的美谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.20,0:22:50.33,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}如同就要失去这副身躯一般
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.50,0:22:59.51,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}在极限的边缘 跌入悲伤的深渊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.77,0:00:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 是我的失误
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我找到了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.07,0:00:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把世界的扭曲…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们要用Gundam来破坏世界的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想得美!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.16,0:00:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.41,0:00:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Throne的改进型?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.66,0:00:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道说?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.83,0:00:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 让我们开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之间的壮丽杀戮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和之前不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过瘾啊 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:00:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还活着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.53,0:01:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 但是托你的福 身体的一半都变成焦炭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.67,0:01:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子的命还不够还啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.38,0:01:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用你小子的命来付再生治疗的帐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OO和Seravee似乎进入战斗状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是被A-LAWS逮到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.95,0:03:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着Gundam果然是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,联络待命中的阿雷鲁亚他们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.79,0:03:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.46,0:03:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 库尔吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋是洛克昂的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来洗刷你的罪孽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.40,0:03:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他那是自作自受
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明右眼看不到 还上战场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隐藏手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲开了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.96,0:03:55.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:03:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快给我上西天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援军?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4对1吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底还是不好对付
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 提艾利亚 斯米拉琪小姐下达归舰命令了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.51,0:04:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阻止我!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是洛克昂的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥的…仇人?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,库尔吉斯的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:10.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是难缠的小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过呢 不这样的话不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里杰诺…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 宴会一团糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.31,0:05:33.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把提艾利亚·爱德惹怒的可是你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明只要好好款待 就能让他成为我们的同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.44,0:05:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟蹋了我的一片苦心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们好像想与我们对抗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.78,0:05:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者的活动越剧烈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS就越会被舆论所接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其行动也可以正当化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是挺好吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手只有KATARON的话 就太没意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,专职战斗的我也就没有出场的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TWIN DRIVE系统
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.59,0:06:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭载两个GN DRIVE的Gundam是天行者独立开发的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.23,0:06:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和TRANS-AM系统一样 是伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的遗产呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是什么 都无所谓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种程度的性能 远不及Gadessa
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下次的战斗中 里瓦夫·里维尔就能给我们证明了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要给我出场的机会哦 里本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那他们好像全身而退了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和监视者的对立 将加速变革的前进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准尉 感觉好些了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.11,0:07:08.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让您挂心了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.20,0:07:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于我的身体 不准备问我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望我问吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到部队就会展开Gundam的追击战
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁现在多休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.34,0:07:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝·哈勒维…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4年前由于Gundam的攻击 失去了所有的家人和亲属
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自身也暴露在有毒性的GN粒子之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得了细胞再生障碍症
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.62,0:07:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,年纪轻轻就进入战场的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是个更适合美丽裙子的楚楚少女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.13,0:08:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个青年是天行者的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那·F·塞艾…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个机体…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.武士道!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各机收容完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部GN DRIVE与托勒密的接续作业开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到宇宙去?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照我的预测 12小时以内 敌人就会布下包围网
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候就逃不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 到拉格朗日点L3去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:44.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以维护Gundam 并接收支援机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.88,0:08:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 米蕾娜 能开始准备脱离大气圈的工作么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.75,0:08:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇见露易丝了?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶然碰上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她好么?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.06,0:09:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.89,0:09:05.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打听了你的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你在天上工作
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有联络吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架Gundam是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 哥哥的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是字面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶那架Gundam的亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯 夺取了洛克昂的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里·阿鲁·沙歇斯?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我详情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.39,0:09:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米卢诺夫少尉和哈勒维准尉平安归舰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.81,0:09:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即由Gundam的消失地点、经过时间、移动速度方面考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推测敌舰在这附近的海底航行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我方部队以6架Trilobite包围这个区域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现后即展开攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.99,0:10:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制空权的保障呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2只MS小队就足够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为估计他们不会从海底出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想对这个战术发表些不同的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:17.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘记了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:22.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰可是突破大气层而降落地面的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 相反的行动是不是也可以呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是同样的看法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的GN DRIVE拥有\N被称作TRANS-AM的高浓度粒子全面解放的系统
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用那个的话 恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:41.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好与静止卫星轨道上的部队进行合作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌方的作战指挥官 应该也预见到了刚才正统的战术了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放肆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算愚弄我这个长官吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有许可
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.79,0:10:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下也是个人部队吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Mr.武士道不同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.09,0:11:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我答应大佐 会遵从您的战术指示
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.05,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太感谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.52,0:11:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥为了报家人的仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.35,0:11:13.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才和那个叫沙歇斯的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.06,0:11:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起世界的变革 更在乎私人恩怨吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是像哥哥的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不满么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是觉得尊敬他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.87,0:11:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人去世是十多年前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说耿耿于怀如此长久我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.17,0:11:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算仇人就站在这里也一样么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.21,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾隶属于KPSA…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个夺去了你们家人生命的组织
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用连那种事情都说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有不能不说的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要代替神去完成使命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.40,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 会死的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么 你小子? 死很可怕吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是亵渎神明的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.70,0:12:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在神明之前奉上的一场圣战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于无视传统 荒废神明土地的非信仰者们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为神之代理的我等将给予裁决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.97,0:12:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候 要是我能阻止同伴的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克昂…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 尼尔·狄兰迪…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就不会成为机师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.40,0:12:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你阻止了他 恐怖袭击还是会发生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情的发展不会有变化的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切 都是过去的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算悔恨过去也无济于事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我们并不是为了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.79,0:12:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了未来才战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贯彻着自己的正义而活着…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.68,0:13:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那样能够通向真正的未来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同变革者的敌对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着真正的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.07,0:13:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是在开发新型机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古拉哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 现在是Mr.武士道对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便那样称呼 为难之致
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你很中意那名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 今天来是有什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来对阁下就任开发主任一事表达祝贺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 还在试验阶段的那架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能划归于吾之名下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.68,0:13:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来这才是来这里的本意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么要求么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祈望最速之躯及最强之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉从尊意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为交换 希望你能确实地了结他们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在只是为此而活
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.71,0:14:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你所属的部队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在应该在作战行动中…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:27.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对舰队战没什么兴趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连作战方式都看穿了么…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心眼在时刻锻炼之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS队 全体出击
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trilobite各机
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.39,0:14:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已到达索敌区域
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 捕捉到敌舰同时开始作战
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.57,0:14:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和本作战没有任何关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请您认识到这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.95,0:14:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悉随尊便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.29,0:15:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是 Gadessa…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是新型机么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS预算的规模究竟有多大…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 会怎么登场呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有报告给斯米拉琪·李·诺莉艾卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 正在整理想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.19,0:15:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我当时之后发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你发现的歪曲究竟是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.79,0:15:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革就会伴随着伤痛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不也是一直这样过来的么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少罗嗦两句直接去做不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了计划而诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是被伊奥利亚老爹寄托了Gundam的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们现在是伊奥利亚计划的阻碍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军 水下MA 6架已确认
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.31,0:16:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各乘员 请到达指定位置
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.06,0:16:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.11,0:16:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.52,0:16:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人正包围着托勒密逐步接近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测攻击开始时间呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.28,0:16:14.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0024的说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在赤道上被敌人预测到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.95,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一手啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在辅助席上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来就没那么好过了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.46,0:16:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号 进入急速上浮姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.47,0:16:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下中东那样不管回到宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:41.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了从A-LAWS手中逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测攻击时间之后又过了0004的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等等
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后一刻都要引他们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军部队有反应了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是大型鱼雷!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arios Cherudim Seravee
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.91,0:16:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM启动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:16:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.03,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力场最大展开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号紧急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.33,0:17:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到爆炸的上方去!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛祖保佑吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.63,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}南無三：佛教用语「南无三宝」的略称
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密号进入飞行模式!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰 向海面紧急上浮
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.94,0:17:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并继续上升
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.27,0:17:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那… 那些家伙真的想突破大气层么!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我预测得还快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将Trilobite的攻击作为初加速度利用了么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计算敌舰的上升路线
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.75,0:17:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这 这种速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不是舰艇的速度…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明… 明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没什么用啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.43,0:18:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全炮门 打开
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.14,0:18:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全弹发射!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么又这样!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等大胆的战术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.95,0:18:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前进轨道 计算出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里维尔大尉!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上升角度的变化仅仅只有3度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这架Gasessa来说小菜一碟!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高度突破600千米
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样脱离大气层
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.82,0:18:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角度被改变了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军指挥官 真的有一手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一幕 结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.95,0:19:05.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军TRANS-AM系统有限制时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:08.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 就看杰江中佐的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密 高度1万千米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.00,0:19:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已越过低轨道环
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军的攻击!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是伏兵!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM 超过限制时间
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再填充之前 GN力场消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.93,0:19:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰体上部中弹!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军的数量是!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.06,0:19:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军 巡洋舰1艘   MS 6架!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也在预测之内呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军的粒子量已用尽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.16,0:19:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口气干掉他们!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军MS 接近!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.83,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然有援军!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.00,0:19:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那架机体不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:04.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 在脱离大气层过程中紧急发射的吗!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.68,0:20:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擒贼先擒王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 驱逐目标!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.15,0:20:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰沉默的说!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军MS 剩余4架正在撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.41,0:20:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棋高一着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:37.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:41.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从敌军MS传来了可视通信消息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:43.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消息?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:44.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要读出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.97,0:20:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对天行者 梨莎·久篠的战术表示敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,独立治安维持部队 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯蒂·玛奈金
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.19,0:20:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这条消息
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.27,0:21:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛奈金…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.48,0:21:03.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凯蒂·玛奈金…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 她…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在A-LAWS…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.25,0:21:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.29,0:21:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃不掉了呢 我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那无比憎恨的过去之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.72,0:21:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法拭去的过去之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰江中佐 战死…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再付出牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.50,0:23:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能向「他们」请求援助了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向变革者…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.47,0:23:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向那些超越人类的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.64,0:23:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 这家伙么!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.19,0:23:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,型号GNR-010
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.27,0:23:48.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体名 0 Raiser哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错啊 琳达
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.74,0:23:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这家伙的话 00就是无敌的了!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在对死亡的思考中感知生存
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然则无错之人就无法选择正确之路么
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.54,0:24:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 天之光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 背负起罪孽的天空之辉


